(1593, 5, '2011-10-17 08:53:43', '2011-10-17 08:53:43', 'Ms. Brittain has over fifteen years in the recruiting industry. She brings extensive knowledge in the recruiting industry from managing RPOs and  building client relationships. She has executed and managed many different solutions in her career, including Compaq Computers, Continental Airlines, Kellogg, Hershey''s, Hexion Chemicals and Dell.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ms. Brittain spent eleven years with Recruitment Enhancement Services an Omnicom Group Inc. company, as a Director, Client Services in its recruitment process outsourcing  division.\r\n\r\nMs. Brittain has experience in the areas of recruitment strategy, workflow process, client relationship, technology implementation, vendor relations, metric reports and best practices for achieving an organizations strategic vision and goals.\r\n \r\nAdditionally, Ms. Brittain has worked in various industries such as Consumer Packaged Goods, Specialty Chemicals, Manufacturing, Financial Services, Petroleum, Defense, Government, Information Technology, Engineering Construction,  and Advertising/Marketing.\r\n \r\nMs. Brittain graduated from Texas A&M in 1991 with a Bachelors degree.', 'Dena Brittain', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dena-brittain', '', '', '2011-10-17 16:39:44', '2011-10-17 16:39:44', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1593', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
