(238, 1, '2011-10-17 14:32:33', '2011-10-17 14:32:33', '<p>In a volatile and fiercely competitive world, businesses and organizations of all kinds need to identify, recruit and retain talent with impact. Futurestep Recruitment Process Outsourcing (RPO) provides the optimal solution.</p>\n\n<p>\nRPO delivers a number of key benefits:\n<ul>\n<li>Better and more cost effective processes</li>\n<li>Reductions in cost and time to hire and more control over both</li>\n<li>Access to scalable, flexible talent resources</li>\n<li>Enhanced employer brand and corporate reputation</li>\n<li>More responsive workforce planning</li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nOver the past 13 years we’ve established ourselves as RPO specialists, delivering solutions that make a positive commercial impact for our clients. We’ve extended our global network and the breadth of our offer to cover almost every industry sector and specialist functions, with a particular focus on mid and senior level managerial technical talent.\n\nFuturestep delivers talent with impact because we invest in the best: the best professionals in our industry and through Korn/Ferry the most advanced recruitment tools and processes – standardized to suit the needs of multinational organizations and yet sensitive to local characteristics.', 'Recruitment Process Outsourcing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-autosave', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:32:33', '2011-10-17 14:32:33', '', 11, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
