(1557, 4, '2011-10-14 11:28:04', '2011-10-14 11:28:04', 'Futurestep is pleased to announce that we are a RPO Host Sponsor of the 2011 HRO Summit Europe, inBarcelona,Spainon 2nd – 4th November 2011.\n\nThe event is hosted by SharedXpertise, a community of Human Resource business professionals, and is part of the HRO Today Forum series of global events. HRO Summit Europe is the largest and most comprehensive human resources outsourcing and operations conference in Europe, and this year’s event will feature workshops and sessions focused on the summit’s theme of “HR Change Agents: empowering the HR professional to lead and transform business through HRO.” More than 250 senior executives including Chief HR Officers, vice presidents of HR and Shared Services Management, and executives from finance, IT and other areas that need to take advantage of the evolution of the HR function – will be exchanging views on managing global operations and improving the business value of HR.', 'HRO Summit Europe 2011, Barcelona', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1554-revision-2', '', '', '2011-10-14 11:28:04', '2011-10-14 11:28:04', '', 1554, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1555, 5, '2011-10-17 08:46:57', '2011-10-17 08:46:57', 'Tanya Bennett is the Global Operations Leader for Recruitment Process Outsourcing for Futurestep. She joined the company''s North America team in 2002 as the Director of Managed Services.\n\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ms. Bennett worked for Corestaff Services as Vice President of Performance Partnerships. Overseeing programs that accounted for approximately $400 million in revenue, her diversified client base included financial services, healthcare, industrial practices, technical and business services.\n\nMs. Bennett has 20 years of experience in the staffing industry, including onsite and project staffing, as well as extensive operations management. She began her career in 1987 with Talent Tree Personnel as a Staffing Consultant and was later named Regional Services Director.\n\nMs. Bennett graduated from Ripon College in Wisconsin with a bachelor’s degree in English and Business Management.\n', 'Tanya Bennett', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'tanya-bennett-2', '', '', '2011-10-17 08:49:14', '2011-10-17 08:49:14', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1555', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
(1556, 4, '2011-10-14 11:25:01', '2011-10-14 11:25:01', 'Futurestep is pleased to announce that we are a RPO Host Sponsor of the 2011 HRO Summit Europe, inBarcelona,Spainon 2nd – 4th November 2011. As part of this sponsorship, we have the opportunity to invite selected guests with an interest in HR outsourcing to attend the event free of charge, and we would like to extend this invitation to you.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe event is hosted by SharedXpertise, a community of Human Resource business professionals, and is part of the HRO Today Forum series of global events. HRO Summit Europe is the largest and most comprehensive human resources outsourcing and operations conference in Europe, and this year’s event will feature workshops and sessions focused on the summit’s theme of “HR Change Agents: empowering the HR professional to lead and transform business through HRO.” More than 250 senior executives including Chief HR Officers, vice presidents of HR and Shared Services Management, and executives from finance, IT and other areas that need to take advantage of the evolution of the HR function – will be exchanging views on managing global operations and improving the business value of HR.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe hope you will take advantage of this offer and join us in Barcelona.', 'HRO Summit Europe 2011, Barcelona', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1554-revision', '', '', '2011-10-14 11:25:01', '2011-10-14 11:25:01', '', 1554, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
