(365, 1, '2011-09-08 16:40:52', '2011-09-08 16:40:52', '<p>In a competitive and fast developing marketplace, our Consumer team provides talent acquisition services, including strategic and transformation advice, to many of the world&#39;s leading consumer businesses, including food manufacturers, consumer electronics and luxury brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The team offers a wealth and breadth of expertise unmatched in our industry: seasoned recruitment professionals and specialists with priceless &#39;client-side’&#39; experience in the consumer sectors. Typically, we help businesses recruit into:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regional and country level management roles</li>\r\n	<li>Sales</li>\r\n	<li>Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>HR</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Our clients range from large global corporates through to SMEs or small start-ups. They all choose us because they know we can consistently deliver the very best talent.</p>\r\n', 'Consumer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'consumer', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:25:11', '2011-10-17 15:25:11', '', 265, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?page_id=365', 16, 'page', '', 0),
(366, 1, '2011-09-08 16:40:41', '2011-09-08 16:40:41', '', 'Consumer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '365-revision', '', '', '2011-09-08 16:40:41', '2011-09-08 16:40:41', '', 365, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(367, 1, '2011-09-08 16:41:34', '2011-09-08 16:41:34', '<p>Our specialist financial services team works with many of the world’&#39;s leading banks, insurers and financial services businesses – delivering talent with impact: recruitment solutions that have tangible impact on their performance and competitiveness.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our experience and research-driven approach allows us to identify the best candidates for every role. The use of proven interview and assessment tools enables us to achieve some of the highest delivery and placement rates in the search industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nOur team includes experts who can provide advice and deliver talent in a range of roles and functions, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Front office</li>\r\n<li>Sales</li>\r\n<li>Finance</li>\r\n<li>Risk</li>\r\n<li>Legal and compliance</li>\r\n<li>Operations and technology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>', 'Financial Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'financial-services', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:10:37', '2011-10-17 15:10:37', '', 265, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?page_id=367', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(368, 1, '2011-09-08 16:41:30', '2011-09-08 16:41:30', '', 'Financial Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '367-revision', '', '', '2011-09-08 16:41:30', '2011-09-08 16:41:30', '', 367, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(369, 1, '2011-09-08 16:41:45', '2011-09-08 16:41:45', '<p>A competitive manufacturing sector is now considered an essential prerequisite for sustainable prosperity, but over the past few years we have witnessed a significant shift in the global economy  - with industrial growth in emerging economies gaining pace while industrial capacity in mature economies contracts but becomes increasingly productive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One consequence of this shift is that engineering and other industrial firms are shifting their talent capacity to support a move into emerging markets. This shift demands greater talent mobility and has seen talent community become increasingly global in nature, with project leadership and business impact skills at a premium.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nOur Industrial team has the expertise to help businesses access the technical and commercial talent they need to succeed in a changing world. The team’&#39;s experience spans key sectors, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Construction</li>\r\n	<li>Infrastructure</li>\r\n	<li>Oil and gas</li>\r\n	<li>Energy</li>\r\n	<li>Automotive</li>\r\n	<li>Manufacturing</li>\r\n	<li>Defense and Aerospace</li>\r\n	<li>Mining and transportation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>', 'Industrial', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'industrial', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:16:00', '2011-10-17 15:16:00', '', 265, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?page_id=369', 4, 'page', '', 0),
