(371, 1, '2011-09-08 16:42:05', '2011-09-08 16:42:05', '<p>The discovery and delivery of impactful talent is an essential pre-requisite for growth and leadership in the life sciences sector. In a competitive marketplace, our Life Sciences team provides talent acquisition services to many of key players and leading life science brands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The team offers a wealth and breadth of expertise unmatched in our industry: seasoned recruitment professionals and specialists with priceless &#39;client-side&#39; experience who understand that talent must &#39;fit&#39; in terms of both function and culture. We cover a wide range of sub-sectors – pharmaceuticals, medical devices, diagnostics, biotech, clinical research organizations, consultancies and service providers – typically helping clients to recruit into\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Regional and country level management roles</li>\r\n		<li>Medical</li>\r\n		<li>R&D</li>\r\n		<li>Operations</li>\r\n		<li>Sales</li>\r\n		<li>Marketing</li>\r\n		<li>Finance</li>\r\n		<li>Procurement</li>\r\n		<li>HR</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our clients range from large global corporates through to SMEs or small biotech start-ups. They all choose us because they know we can consistently deliver the very best talent.</p>\r\n', 'Life Sciences', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'life-sciences', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:21:18', '2011-10-17 15:21:18', '', 265, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?page_id=371', 8, 'page', '', 0),
