(599, 1, '2011-10-17 14:36:28', '2011-10-17 14:36:28', '<p>\r\nFuturestep understands that the world is unpredictable. Successful businesses plan for the future, but the future has a habit of throwing up ‘curve balls’. Situations in which you need to recruit talent in a niche specialism or a part of the world where you have limited access to the best. In these situations Futurestep project recruitment solutions make the difference.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nUtilizing a tried and tested recruitment methodology, we can deliver the right talent in the right numbers and in the right location – over a timeframe agreed in advance with you. Our consultant teams ensure that the process is seamless, stress-free and constructed to dovetail with your broader talent acquisition strategy.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nFuturestep project recruitment solutions give you:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dedicated support – a team leader who manages all outsourcing on your behalf, from sourcing and research through screening and selection</li>\r\n<li>A bespoke recruitment strategy – tailored to meet your needs and match your culture and processes</li>\r\n<li>Time-sensitive recruitment processes – delivering the right talent in good time, with no compromises on quality or efficiency</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>', 'Project Recruitment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '386-autosave', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:36:28', '2011-10-17 14:36:28', '', 386, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1682, 5, '2011-10-17 14:33:41', '2011-10-17 14:33:41', 'Ms. Matthews, Consulting Director for Futurestep, has more than 12 years of experience on consulting projects both globally and regionally helping clients improve the effectiveness of their Talent Acquisition and HR systems. \n\nMs. Matthews is a goal-oriented, results-driven leader with a strong background in talent management/talent acquisition systems, change management, project management, process analysis, workforce planning and business process outsourcing.\n \nFormerly, Ms. Matthews was a Senior Recruiting Manager providing management and business consulting expertise to internal clients globally in the area of talent management/acquisition. Prior to a Sr. Recruiting Manager, she was a Project Lead, Global HR Solutions at ACS. In this role, Ms. Matthews was responsible for managing and implementing ATS for her clients. This work included implementation of standardized integrations, identifying resources required and duration to execute against financial benefits, risks and impacts of doing the implementations. Kenyatta also held the roles of Human Resources Manager and Lead Recruiter with previous employers.\n\nMs. Matthews holds a Bachelor of Arts in Social Work from St. Edwards University in Austin, TX.\n', 'Kenyatta Matthews', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1680-revision', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:33:41', '2011-10-17 14:33:41', '', 1680, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(742, 1, '2011-10-17 14:38:21', '2011-10-17 14:38:21', '\n Discovering the best talent – talent that will positively impact your business – is probably the single most pressing recruitment challenge that successful multinational businesses face today. Futurestep is uniquely positioned and equipped to help them meet this challenge more effectively.\n\nFuturestep is a truly global business, with 38 offices across 19 countries and an extensive global talent database that spans all major industries and key functions. At the same time, with more than 800 recruitment consultants operating ‘in country’ Futurestep is incredibly sensitive to local circumstances and requirements. \n\nIn addition to our extensive global capacity and local sensitivity we add a third strength: specialist expertise – with every one of our consultants providing invaluable experience and understanding in six key vertical segments: industrial, technology, life sciences, financial services, government and consumer.\n', 'Search', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '388-autosave', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:38:21', '2011-10-17 14:38:21', '', 388, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
