(631, 1, '2011-10-07 11:17:19', '2011-10-07 11:17:19', 'hen it comes to putting your talent management strategy into practice, the details of technical support can require significant time, effort and resources. To ensure the success of your solutions, as well as the processes that they enable, Futurestep provides support for key areas of talent management technology implementation, including data migration, data integration and reporting and metrics.\n<h4>Data Migration:\nMinimize the Time and Costs of Transitioning Data into New Processes</h4>\nAs many recruiting and talent management decision makers know, transitioning data into new processes and systems can be costly and time consuming. Futurestep minimizes the burden of data migration by helping you take control of the process. We can oversee the data conversion and migration process, and develop applications to facilitate smooth transition, putting data in the hands of the people who need it, quickly and effectively.\n<h4>Data Integration:\nConnect External Systems with Your Internal HR Applications</h4>\nThere are advantages in integrating internally hosted systems and Internet-based talent management solutions. You can achieve more accurate data capture for applicant information, less duplication of data entry for requisition data or resumes and decreased cycle time for hiring, but the integration task can be costly and time consuming. Futurestep can take the pain out of the integration process, reduce the associated risk, and help you realize the ROI you seek from your technology investments.\n<h4>Reporting and Metrics:\nIdentify and Capture the Metrics that Matter</h4>\nFuturestep provides the most effective process available today for pinpointing the metrics that matter and transforming those metrics into reports that will capture your talent management success. The most important ingredient to an effective reporting strategy is an objective process that accommodates your unique needs and conditions and applies them to a framework for arriving at reports that reflect both industry best practices and your business objectives.', 'Technology', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '382-autosave', '', '', '2011-10-07 11:17:19', '2011-10-07 11:17:19', '', 382, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
