(782, 2, '2011-10-06 11:04:03', '2011-10-06 11:04:03', 'The Global Technology Markets practice at Futurestep covers the following sub sectors; Software, Hardware, Telecommunications, Networking, Technology Consulting, Professional Services and Media Services. Within each of the sub-sectors we recruit across all job functions for our clients, these include;\r\n\r\nRegional Vice Presidents\r\n\r\nCountry MD''s and leaders\r\n\r\nCIO''s and IT Directors\r\n\r\nOperations\r\n\r\nMarketing\r\n\r\nHR\r\n\r\nSales\r\n\r\nMarketing\r\n\r\nFinance\r\n\r\nTechnologists\r\n\r\nProcurement\r\n\r\nOur clients range from the largest blue chip corporate through to mid-size and SME organisations down to Private equity backed and start-up companies. They all have the need to hire exceptional talent to maintain or gain competitive advantage in the fastest moving sector on the globe. Quite simply, those organisations who can find, attract, retain and develop their talent will be the market leaders of the future.\r\n\r\nOur Consultants have worked within the Global Technology Markets since the early nineties as recruitment professionals or within the client side of the industry itself. This brings an unparallel experience to our teams. Our GTM researchers are multi-lingual and have deep sector experience combined with utilising the best recruitment tools within the industry today.\r\n\r\nAcross the world, Futurestep provides its recruitment services and expertise to some of the most well known technology brands. We have an incredible amount of knowledge within technology markets, which enables us to deliver candidates of exceptional quality that mean we consistently exceed client expectations.', 'Technology', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '373-revision-7', '', '', '2011-10-06 11:04:03', '2011-10-06 11:04:03', '', 373, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
