(863, 2, '2011-10-10 10:41:53', '2011-10-10 10:41:53', 'Recruitment process outsourcing (RPO) offers the optimal solution to managing challenging resourcing requirements in today‚Äôs volatile economies.\r\n\r\nOperational benefits include process efficiencies and access to expert, flexible, scalable resources. Our clients see significant financial benefits, not just in terms of reduction in cost and time to hire, but through much greater visibility and control of recruitment costs. And working in partnership with our clients we are able to help them realise strategic benefits such as implementing a proactive workforce planning process, reinforcing their employer brand and increasing the quality of talent brought into the business.\r\n\r\nFuturestep has over 13 years experience in developing and building bespoke outsourced recruitment solutions that make a positive commercial impact to our clients. We have an extensive global network, in-depth sector expertise and a wide range of complementary consulting solutions. We employ only the most experienced and innovative recruitment professionals, and as a part of the Korn/Ferry group, incorporate the most sophisticated and developed recruitment tools and expertise into our processes.', 'Recruitment Process Outsourcing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-53', '', '', '2011-10-10 10:41:53', '2011-10-10 10:41:53', '', 11, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
