(867, 1, '2011-10-17 14:47:00', '2011-10-17 14:47:00', '<p>To deliver on corporate strategy successful businesses understand the need to discover, acquire and measure talent with impact – now and in future. Building on our vast experience, we bring logic and clarity to this challenge: starting with a clear understanding of corporate strategy and its implications for talent in the broadest sense before developing a coherent action plan to discover, deliver and maximize the right talent to put strategy into practice.</p>\n\n<p>\nWe can help you to create and implement a workforce planning strategy and program that meets the unique needs of your business, focusing on the issues that matter most to you:\n</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Understanding the talent market better</li>\n<li>Quantifying the skills you will need in future</li>\n<li>Interpreting talent metrics</li>\n<li>Identifying and rectifying talent gaps</li>\n<li>Determining a coherent action plan to maximize Talent with Impact</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>\nWhether you ask us to help you address one or all of these issues, we will put in place a workforce planning team that really understands your business and works for its long-term success, not just a short-term goal.\n</p>', 'Workforce Planning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '384-autosave', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:47:00', '2011-10-17 14:47:00', '', 384, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1688, 1, '2011-10-10 10:53:08', '2011-10-10 10:53:08', '<h3><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal;">More and more often, clients look to outsource the entirety of their resourcing and talent functions to AMS having first engaged us for a particular project, region or business unit.</span></h3>\r\nClients choose to do this in a number of ways. For instance, they might engage us as an RPO provider to manage permanent and graduate recruitment, an executive search firm to manage senior hiring, a managed services provider to handle the contingent workforce, and other agencies to handle ad-hoc staffing.\r\n\r\nBut ensuring that all parties are fully aligned, working in unison, and actively managing the employer brand effectively can be particularly challenging. Providers negotiate different terms of service, operate differently, engage with disparate areas of the organisation, and work to their own agenda. Even under a master vendor agreement, where one organisation takes responsibility for managing all service providers, differences in service levels and operating models mean an inconsistent engagement and a mismatched solution.\r\n\r\nWith a scope of services that extends far beyond the traditional outsourcing remit, and with documented experience in delivering complex, multi-discipline solutions, Alexander Mann Solutions can provide an option that resolves the workforce acquisition dilemma. We call this Total Workforce Acquisition (TWA), and it covers every part of the resourcing and talent landscape.', 'Workforce Planning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '384-revision-9', '', '', '2011-10-10 10:53:08', '2011-10-10 10:53:08', '', 384, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
