(886, 2, '2011-10-10 13:36:55', '2011-10-10 13:36:55', 'Marisa Kacary is Global Vice President of Marketing for Futurestep and leads marketing programs across all regions. Responsible for the continuing growth of Futurestep‚Äôs brand, Marisa is intent on building upon Futurestep‚Äôs ranking as the global leader in strategic talent acquisition solutions as it expands its range of consulting services globally.\n\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Marisa was Director of Marketing and Communications for RPO provider Alexander Mann Solutions (AMS). Here she led all external and internal marketing on a global basis for the business. Before joining AMS, Marisa was responsible for marketing at Capital Consulting, a global pure-play RPO provider acquired by AMS in February 2008. At Capital Consulting, she led the re-brand of the organisation, including strategy and development of all external and internal communications.\n\nMarisa spent the early part of her career in the IT and telco sector, working in marketing roles for organizations such as Cable and Wireless, Compaq and Nortel Networks. Her experience in recruitment marketing began at professional recruitment consultancy Robert Walters, where she was the Marketing Manager for the UK, Continental Europe, the US and South Africa; here she also managed the marketing for the Resource Solutions and Interim Leaders brands.\n\nMarisa is a graduate of Durham University with a bachelor‚Äôs degree in Geography.¬† She is a member of the Chartered Institute of Marketing (CIM) and holds a CIM Diploma', 'Marisa Kackary', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '855-revision-3', '', '', '2011-10-10 13:36:55', '2011-10-10 13:36:55', '', 855, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
