(1465, 2, '2011-10-12 17:53:40', '2011-10-12 17:53:40', 'The Futurestep story starts in back in 1969 when Lester Korn and Richard Ferry founded Korn/Ferry International in the US. Their company grew from success to success throughout the 1970s, moving beyond the US into Europe, the Middle East, Asia, Latin America and the Asia Pacific region to become the world’s largest executive search firm by 2006 (Fortune Magazine).\r\n\r\nFuturestep was created in 1998 as a direct response to market demand for flexible, customized recruitment solutions – specifically recruitment process outsourcing (RPO), project recruitment, search and consulting. Today, our business is recognized as a global leader in its own right.\r\n\r\n<em>Futurestep key facts:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Created in 1998 to deliver scalable outsourcing solutions for Korn/Ferry</li>\r\n	<li>800+ Futurestep professionals working out of 38 offices in 19 countries</li>\r\n	<li>Successful relationships with one in three Fortune 100 companies</li>\r\n	<li>Extensive experience across all major industry sectors and functions</li>\r\n	<li>Consistent recognition from peers and clients:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Listed by HRO (2009 – 2011)</li>\r\n	<li>Included in Baker’s Dozen list of global RPO providers and their global leader for ‘Breadth of Service’ in 2011</li>\r\n	<li>Listed in the Black Book of Outsourcers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '506-revision-13', '', '', '2011-10-12 17:53:40', '2011-10-12 17:53:40', '', 506, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
