(1583, 4, '2011-10-14 12:12:52', '2011-10-14 12:12:52', '<a href="http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/news-events/hro-summit-europe-2011-barcelona-2/attachment/hroa-title3" rel="attachment wp-att-1558"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1558" title="HRO logo" src="http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/HROA-title3.jpg" alt="" width="465" height="125" /></a> \r\n\r\nFuturestep is pleased to announce that we are a RPO Host Sponsor of the 2011 HRO Summit Europe, in Barcelona, Spain on 2nd – 4th November 2011.\r\n\r\nThe event is hosted by SharedXpertise, a community of Human Resource business professionals, and is part of the HRO Today Forum series of global events. HRO Summit Europe is the largest and most comprehensive human resources outsourcing and operations conference in Europe, and this year’s event will feature workshops and sessions focused on the summit’s theme of “HR Change Agents: empowering the HR professional to lead and transform business through HRO.” More than 250 senior executives including Chief HR Officers, vice presidents of HR and Shared Services Management, and executives from finance, IT and other areas that need to take advantage of the evolution of the HR function – will be exchanging views on managing global operations and improving the business value of HR.', 'HRO Summit Europe 2011, Barcelona', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1554-revision-14', '', '', '2011-10-14 12:12:52', '2011-10-14 12:12:52', '', 1554, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
