(1601, 5, '2011-10-17 09:03:32', '2011-10-17 09:03:32', 'Mrs. Cade joined Futurestep in 2002 as a Recruiter quickly advancing to a Senior Recruiter and has served in a management role since 2004. Currently, a Project Director in our Projects division, Mrs. Cade is responsible for the deployment of recruitment management solutions, specializing in the Consumer and Industrial practices. She works with global and national clients utilizing best practices and the latest recruitment process efficiencies in each project she manages. \r\n\r\nFurther, Mrs. Cade has managed global projects, client relationships and teams of centralized and decentralized Recruiters and Administrative staff.  \r\n\r\nMrs. Cade has provided exceptional service delivery for Futurestep clients to include: Halliburton, General Mills, Kraft, Hilton, Rio Tinto, Yum Restaurants International, Goodyear Tire and Rubber, Palm, Morgan Stanley Smith Barney, Response Genetics and Wal-Mart.\r\n\r\nPrior to Joining Futurestep, Mrs. Cade was a Senior Consultant with a boutique executive search firm focusing on the recruitment and placement of Executive and Mid-Management talent in the consumer, financial services, manufacturing, publishing and telecommunication industries.  Germayne excels at understanding client expectations, motivating her team to perform beyond those expectations, consulting with the client throughout the project and managing through continuous improvement. \r\n\r\nMrs. Cade holds a Bachelor of Arts in Political Science from Western Illinois University in Macomb, Illinois.\r\n', 'Germayne Cade', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1595-revision-2', '', '', '2011-10-17 09:03:32', '2011-10-17 09:03:32', '', 1595, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
