(1620, 5, '2011-10-17 10:02:21', '2011-10-17 10:02:21', 'Ms. Ho is a Managing Consultant and is responsible for client development and delivery of the Search business in Canada.\r\n\r\nMs. Ho excels at understanding client expectations, consulting with the client throughout the search process and delivering top talent through search process rigger and leveraging her extensive\r\nprofessional network.\r\n\r\nMs. Ho started at Futurestep as a Senior Recruiter with responsibility for single search client deliverables. She has been responsible for providing exceptional service delivery for Futurestep clients including: Insurance Corporation of BC, Viterra, New Gold, WhiteWater West Industries, British Columbia Automobile Association and Ballard Power Systems.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ms. Ho’s brings over five years of diverse experience in various industries such as information technology, government agencies, crown corporations, professional services and hospitality/tourism; positions included senior leadership roles in human resources where she was responsible for key deliverables in talent acquisition, compensation and benefits management, training and development, performance management and various human resources and corporate communication system implementations.\r\n\r\nMs. Ho earned an MBA from Royal Roads University in 2006 and holds a\r\nBachelor of Arts in Applied Communications from Simon Fraser University. She also has completed executive education in leadership and negotiation from the Wharton School at the University of Pennsylvania and Harvard Business School.', 'Nancy Ho', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nancy-ho', '', '', '2011-10-17 17:24:05', '2011-10-17 17:24:05', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1620', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
