(1628, 5, '2011-10-17 10:19:38', '2011-10-17 10:19:38', 'Mr. Keane is a Managing Consultant in the Futurestep New York Office and brings with him more than twenty years of experience in the financial services industry, including product and brand marketing and business development, sales and operations.\r\n\r\nHis extensive network of professionals in the industry coupled with his work history enables him to effectively understand and deliver against client needs.\r\n\r\nWith six years of experience in Executive Search, Mr. Keane has partnered with top national financial institutions, credit card companies and processors, emerging payments companies and e-commerce providers. He came to Futurestep from another national search firm where he managed its New York office and also worked on senior level searches with Financial Institutions and E-Commerce providers.\r\n\r\nPrior to entering executive search, Mr. Keane spent twelve years at MasterCard International, managing some of their largest bank clients and developed customer level brand and marketing strategies. He has  also worked for J.P. Morgan Chase and GE Capital.\r\n \r\nMr. Keane graduated from Fairfield University in Connecticut with a Bachelor of Science in Marketing and Information Systems. Also, he received his MBA in Marketing and Corporate Finance from Pace University Lubin School of Business in New York.', 'Devin Keane', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'devin-keane', '', '', '2011-10-17 10:19:38', '2011-10-17 10:19:38', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1628', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
