(1630, 5, '2011-10-17 10:25:10', '2011-10-17 10:25:10', 'Ms. Le joined Futurestep in 2011 as Solutions Architect supporting RPO Implementation & Projects in the US. In her current role as Program Manager, she is responsible for creating Standard Operating Procedure Manuals for clients, launching Project Implementation and Client Immersion programs, maintaining Project Schedules, and managing the delivery of weekly Operational Reports and Monthly Business Review Reports.\r\n\r\nMs. Le began her RPO career supporting the Shared Services Delivery Team at Credit Suisse in New York City. After that, she worked as an in-house Recruiter at a top global Hedge Fund and has human resources consulting experience across financial services, publishing, and media firms. \r\n\r\nShe holds a BA in Psychology with a double minor in Communications & Music from the University of California at Davis and a Masters in Social-Organizational Psychology at Columbia University.\r\n', 'Hong Le', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hong-le', '', '', '2011-10-17 10:25:10', '2011-10-17 10:25:10', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1630', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
