(1636, 5, '2011-10-17 10:48:57', '2011-10-17 10:48:57', 'Mr. Moghadam joined Futurestep in 2011 and brings significant expertise to the Supply Chain and Financial Services practices.  \r\n\r\nPreviously, Mr. Moghadam was an executive search consultant in the Los Angeles offices of Korn/Ferry International, where he conducted senior-level assignments within the Financial Services, Supply Chain and Industrial practices.  His practice has expanded to include Health Care, technology and retail. \r\n\r\nWith a particularly strong interest in the Supply Chain, logistics and financial officers sectors, Mr. Moghadam has worked with clients ranging from Fortune 500 to fast-growth, early-stage venture and private equity backed companies.\r\n\r\nIn addition to Finance, Mr. Moghadam partnered in recruiting a number of other functional disciplines, including Operations, Banking Compliance, Manufacturing, Marketing, Human Resources, and General Management.\r\n\r\nEarlier in his career, Mr. Moghadam was an Accountant, where he focused on global executive compensation and operations reporting.  He also worked on ERP, systems implementation, design and roll out of management and financial reporting.\r\n\r\nMr. Moghadam received his B.S. degree in Accounting from California State University, Northridge. He and his family reside in Irvine, California.\r\n\r\n', 'Kyle Moghadam', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kyle-moghadam', '', '', '2011-10-17 10:53:16', '2011-10-17 10:53:16', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1636', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
