(1645, 5, '2011-10-17 11:34:33', '2011-10-17 11:34:33', 'Ms. Wolf is a Managing Consultant for Futurestep and is based in the Miami office. As a Managing Consultant, Ms. Wolf acts in a “trusted advisor” relationship with clients which includes, understanding their business, culture and talent acquisition needs; sourcing, screening and managing candidates through the interview process; and as a subject matter expert, providing consultative guidance and advice on recruitment best practices.\r\n\r\nMs. Wolf brings to Futurestep nearly ten years of experience in executive level recruitment. Prior to joining the firm, Ms. Wolf was the Executive Recruiter for Kaplan Higher Education, a $1.5B subsidiary of the Washington Post, and was responsible for the execution of all senior leadership searches.  \r\n\r\nEarlier in her career, Ms. Wolf was the Executive Recruiter for DHL, US a $15.4B express package delivery business. During her tenure she also oversaw all recruitment activity for the US Restructuring of DHL’s domestic delivery business and college recruiting efforts.\r\n\r\nFurther, Ms. Wolf earned a Bachelors of Science in Human and Organizational Development from Vanderbilt University.\r\n', 'Andrea Wolf', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'andrea-wolf', '', '', '2011-10-17 11:36:04', '2011-10-17 11:36:04', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1645', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
