(1651, 5, '2011-10-17 11:53:16', '2011-10-17 11:53:16', 'Mr. Yopp joined Futurestep in 2011 as the Government Practice Director. The role sees him responsible for the RPO and Projects components of Futurestep’s U.S. business. He is a seasoned professional with almost thirty years of experience in the field of talent acquisition and staffing.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Mr. Yopp worked in the government and public sectors for such companies and Booz Allen, SAIC, VeriSign, L3 Communications and ACS/Xerox. \r\n\r\nMr. Yopp has performed as an individual contributor recruiting “C” - level talent and led teams in the areas of recruitment strategy, branding, media mix assessment, ATS evaluation/implementation, high volume recruitment and new employee assimilation.  He has an extensive track record of achieving challenging staffing goals in a time and cost effective manner. \r\n\r\nMr. Yopp holds a Bachelor of Science degree in Government from Nasson College - Springvale, Maine. \r\n\r\n', 'Ivan Yopp', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ivan-yopp', '', '', '2011-10-17 11:53:16', '2011-10-17 11:53:16', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1651', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
(1652, 5, '2011-10-17 11:51:03', '2011-10-17 11:51:03', 'Mr. Yopp joined Futurestep in 2011 as the Government Practice Director. The role sees him responsible for the RPO and Projects components of Futurestep’s U.S. business. He is a seasoned professional with almost thirty years of experience in the field of talent acquisition and staffing.\n\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ivan worked in the government and public sectors for such companies and Booz Allen, SAIC, VeriSign, L3 Communications and ACS/Xerox. \n\nMr. Yopp has performed as an individual contributor recruiting “C” - level talent and led teams in the areas of recruitment strategy, branding, media mix assessment, ATS evaluation/implementation, high volume recruitment and new employee assimilation.  He has an extensive track record of achieving challenging staffing goals in a time and cost effective manner. \n\nIvan holds a Bachelor of Science degree in Government from Nasson College - Springvale, Maine. \n\n', 'Ivan Yopp', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1651-revision', '', '', '2011-10-17 11:51:03', '2011-10-17 11:51:03', '', 1651, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1653, 5, '2011-10-17 12:50:49', '2011-10-17 12:50:49', 'Mr. Heres is a Consulting Director at Futurstep Consulting, a Korn/Ferry company  and a leading provider of talent acquisition and management consulting services to Fortune 500 companies. Bart brings over eighteen years of recruitment management and strategic talent acquisition experience to Futurestep Consulting and its clients.  \r\n\r\nDriven by a process improvement mindset, as both a senior executive and entrepreneur, he has built and led large sourcing & talent acquisition teams for broad-line search firms and boutique specialty practices.  \r\n \r\nMr. Heres is a data and metrics driven business professional led by the implementation of best practices in talent acquisition strategy, operational models, processes & technology, and performance monitoring.  His expertise comes as a result of leading large scale recruitment teams in addition to developing and executing global talent acquisition solutions for clients such as Microsoft, NCR, Coca-Cola, and Philips Consumer Electronics. \r\n\r\nFurther he has designed and implemented standardized interviewing/assessment programs, led diversity recruitment initiatives, and implemented multiple staffing technologies. \r\n\r\nMr. Heres secured a Bachelor of Arts degree in Economics & Business Administration from Furman University in 1983 and a Master of Business Administration degree from Clemson University in 1987.\r\n\r\n', 'Bart Heres', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bart-heres', '', '', '2011-10-17 12:50:49', '2011-10-17 12:50:49', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1653', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
