(1660, 5, '2011-10-17 13:32:38', '2011-10-17 13:32:38', 'Mr. Myers is a Consulting Director with Futurestep, and he has over fifteen years experience in full life cycle recruiting, human resources management, leadership development and technology implementations including recruiting, onboarding, performance management, and succession planning initiatives.  \r\n\r\nThroughout his career in technology and HR environments, Mr. Myers has been a leader and contributor in solving customer’s unique business problems while having responsibility reporting into C-level executive management teams.  Adept at understanding a customer''s unique goals, he is able to align the corporate objectives down to the individual contributor. He is highly focused and results-oriented in supporting complex deliverables, priorities, and positive customer outcomes. \r\n\r\nMr. Myers has had the unique opportunity supporting enterprise customers through the Futurestep Consulting Support Center;  here he has engaged with key POC, end-users and external candidates to resolve time sensitive requests in many customer production environments. Mr. Myers has also recently participated and attended Taleo 11A boot camp where he mastered System Administration skills .  \r\n\r\nSome of Mr. Myers’s clients include Sitel Worldwide, Sallie Mae, Fidelity Information Services, Blue Cross Blue Shield of Florida, First Bank of Puerto Rico, and others.  \r\n\r\nMr. Myers holds a Bachelor of Science in Psychology and a Masters of Science in Industrial/Organizational Psychology from Kansas State University.   \r\n\r\n', 'Chad Myers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chad-myers', '', '', '2011-10-17 13:34:12', '2011-10-17 13:34:12', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1660', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
