(1669, 5, '2011-10-17 14:02:46', '2011-10-17 14:02:46', 'As Vice President, Business Development, Mr. Lomasney has an extensive background in talent strategy and talent management technology, with more than fourteen years of experience in sales and business development for top technology providers. \r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestepin 2010, Mr. Lomasney managed and led sales training for ADP Pre-Employment Services, creating significant new business during his four-year tenure. Notable areas of focus at ADP included leadership of sales teams, development and management of strategic and tactical relationships and training. While at ADP, he helped the company achieve a significant level of success in securing new business revenue and new client partnerships.\r\n\r\nBefore ADP, Mr. Lomasney played a key role in the sales effort for VirtualEdge, helping the company achieve rapid growth leading to its acquisition by ADP.  During his time at VirtualEdge, the company’s clientele grew from eight clients to ninety six in a four-year timeframe. Prior to VirtualEdge, he contributed as a senior sales executive at Taleo (formerly Recruitsoft) where he achieved consistent revenue growth over four years at the company. Prior to Taleo, he spent eight years in successful sales leadership at Neopost, a global shipping and mailing business solutions company.\r\n\r\nMr. Lomasney has been consistently recognized as a top business development producer throughout his career.  He is a graduate of California Polytechnic University.', 'Ed Lomasney', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ed-lomasney', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:02:46', '2011-10-17 14:02:46', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1669', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
