(1686, 5, '2011-10-17 14:55:28', '2011-10-17 14:55:28', 'Ms. Carter has worked for Futurestep''s consulting team since March 2010, within our Support Center providing system administration support to our many global clients.\r\n\r\nPrior to Futurestep Consulting, Ms. Carter worked at Wal-Mart Stores, Inc. for nine years. She began her career in the Recruiting Support area providing system administration, user support and training for the corporate ATS, first Personic, then Deploy Solutions.\r\n\r\nShe then developed and assumed the role of Recruiting Researcher where she assisted Recruiters with the sourcing of candidates for hard-to-fill positions and competitive intelligence initiatives for the corporation.  Next, Ms. Carter moved into the Recruiter role for Wal-Mart’s in-house Temporary Services group, where she hired and managed temporary associates for the corporate office.\r\n\r\nAfter seven years in Recruiting, Ms. Carter transferred to the Sam’s Club division as a Process Management Specialist as part of their Process Management Office where she managed the project process for several corporate projects.\r\n\r\nMs. Carter graduated with her BBA in Human Resource Management from Wichita State University in 2000 and received her MBA from Webster University 2004.', 'Kristen Carter', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kristen-carter', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:55:28', '2011-10-17 14:55:28', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1686', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
(1687, 1, '2011-10-17 14:38:50', '2011-10-17 14:38:50', '<p>Discovering the best talent – talent that will positively impact your business – is probably the single most pressing recruitment challenge that successful multinational businesses face today. Futurestep is uniquely positioned and equipped to help them meet this challenge more effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Futurestep is a truly global business, with 38 offices across 19 countries and an extensive global talent database that spans all major industries and key functions. At the same time, with more than 800 recruitment consultants operating ‘in country’ Futurestep is incredibly sensitive to local circumstances and requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to our extensive global capacity and local sensitivity we add a third strength: specialist expertise – with every one of our consultants providing invaluable experience and understanding in six key vertical segments: industrial, technology, life sciences, financial services, government and consumer.</p>\r\n', 'Search', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '388-revision-9', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:38:50', '2011-10-17 14:38:50', '', 388, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
