(1691, 1, '2011-10-17 14:47:13', '2011-10-17 14:47:13', '<p>To deliver on corporate strategy successful businesses understand the need to discover, acquire and measure talent with impact – now and in future. Building on our vast experience, we bring logic and clarity to this challenge: starting with a clear understanding of corporate strategy and its implications for talent in the broadest sense before developing a coherent action plan to discover, deliver and maximize the right talent to put strategy into practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe can help you to create and implement a workforce planning strategy and program that meets the unique needs of your business, focusing on the issues that matter most to you:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Understanding the talent market better</li>\r\n<li>Quantifying the skills you will need in future</li>\r\n<li>Interpreting talent metrics</li>\r\n<li>Identifying and rectifying talent gaps</li>\r\n<li>Determining a coherent action plan to maximize Talent with Impact</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWhether you ask us to help you address one or all of these issues, we will put in place a workforce planning team that really understands your business and works for its long-term success, not just a short-term goal.\r\n</p>', 'Futurestep Workforce Planning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '384-revision-10', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:47:13', '2011-10-17 14:47:13', '', 384, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
