(1700, 1, '2011-10-05 16:11:18', '2011-10-05 16:11:18', 'hen it comes to putting your talent management strategy into practice, the details of technical support can require significant time, effort and resources. To ensure the success of your solutions, as well as the processes that they enable, Futurestep provides support for key areas of talent management technology implementation, including data migration, data integration and reporting and metrics.\r\n<h4>Data Migration:\r\nMinimize the Time and Costs of Transitioning Data into New Processes</h4>\r\nAs many recruiting and talent management decision makers know, transitioning data into new processes and systems can be costly and time consuming. Futurestep minimizes the burden of data migration by helping you take control of the process. We can oversee the data conversion and migration process, and develop applications to facilitate smooth transition, putting data in the hands of the people who need it, quickly and effectively.\r\n<h4>Data Integration:\r\nConnect External Systems with Your Internal HR Applications</h4>\r\nThere are advantages in integrating internally hosted systems and Internet-based talent management solutions. You can achieve more accurate data capture for applicant information, less duplication of data entry for requisition data or resumes and decreased cycle time for hiring, but the integration task can be costly and time consuming. Futurestep can take the pain out of the integration process, reduce the associated risk, and help you realize the ROI you seek from your technology investments.\r\n<h4>Reporting and Metrics:\r\nIdentify and Capture the Metrics that Matter</h4>\r\nFuturestep provides the most effective process available today for pinpointing the metrics that matter and transforming those metrics into reports that will capture your talent management success. The most important ingredient to an effective reporting strategy is an objective process that accommodates your unique needs and conditions and applies them to a framework for arriving at reports that reflect both industry best practices and your business objectives.', 'Technology', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '382-revision-6', '', '', '2011-10-05 16:11:18', '2011-10-05 16:11:18', '', 382, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1701, 1, '2011-10-17 14:49:25', '2011-10-17 14:49:25', '<p>To deliver on corporate strategy successful businesses understand the need to discover, acquire and measure talent with impact – now and in future. Building on our vast experience, we bring logic and clarity to this challenge: starting with a clear understanding of corporate strategy and its implications for talent in the broadest sense before developing a coherent action plan to discover, deliver and maximize the right talent to put strategy into practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWe can help you to create and implement a workforce planning strategy and program that meets the unique needs of your business, focusing on the issues that matter most to you:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Understanding the talent market better</li>\r\n<li>Quantifying the skills you will need in future</li>\r\n<li>Interpreting talent metrics</li>\r\n<li>Identifying and rectifying talent gaps</li>\r\n<li>Determining a coherent action plan to maximize Talent with Impact</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nWhether you ask us to help you address one or all of these issues, we will put in place a workforce planning team that really understands your business and works for its long-term success, not just a short-term goal.\r\n</p>', 'Workforce Planning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '384-revision-11', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:49:25', '2011-10-17 14:49:25', '', 384, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1702, 1, '2011-10-17 14:55:10', '2011-10-17 14:55:10', '<p>Every business naturally wants the best talent available – but not every business thinks strategically about its position, reputation and competitiveness in the talent marketplace. We work closely with businesses in many different industry sectors and with widely varying talent requirements, to help them understand their ‘employer brand’ better  - utilizing quantitative and qualitative analysis to help them do so.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>We show them how this enhanced understanding can be used to create a compelling employee value proposition. We frequently advice them on the best way to build employer brand awareness in the marketplace by putting in place a coherent communication strategy that makes best use of conventional and emerging social media.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the age of Facebook and Twitter it is vital to remain agile and open-minded. It’s also important to discover talent and bring it onside in ways that allow for the creation of talent communities – networks of interest that keep your employer brand top of mind across a specialist segment, making it easier to bring Talent with Impact into your business.</p>\r\n', 'Candidate Attraction Strategies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'candidate-attraction-strategies', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:57:37', '2011-10-17 14:57:37', '', 263, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?page_id=1702', 2, 'page', '', 0),
