(1704, 5, '2011-10-17 14:42:15', '2011-10-17 14:42:15', 'Ms. Carter has worked for Futurestep''s consulting team since March 2010, within our Support Center providing system administration support to our many global clients.\n\nPrior to Futurestep Consulting, Ms. Carter worked at Wal-Mart Stores, Inc. for nine years. She began her career in the Recruiting Support area providing system administration, user support and training for the corporate ATS, first Personic, then Deploy Solutions.\n\nShe then developed and assumed the role of Recruiting Researcher where she assisted Recruiters with the sourcing of candidates for hard-to-fill positions and competitive intelligence initiatives for the corporation.  Next, Ms. Carter moved into the Recruiter role for Wal-Mart’s in-house Temporary Services group, where she hired and managed temporary associates for the corporate office.\n\nAfter seven years in Recruiting, Ms. Carter transferred to the Sam’s Club division as a Process Management Specialist as part of their Process Management Office where she managed the project process for several corporate projects.\n\nMs. Carter graduated with her BBA in Human Resource Management from Wichita State University in 2000 and received her MBA from Webster University 2004.', 'Kristen Carter', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1686-revision', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:42:15', '2011-10-17 14:42:15', '', 1686, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1705, 5, '2011-10-17 14:59:47', '2011-10-17 14:59:47', 'Ms. Pope, Managing Consultant with Futurestep Consulting, a Korn/Ferry company is a certified Six-Sigma green belt with over 8 years experience in HR system implementation and support, including HR/Payroll, applicant tracking, reporting, performance management and self-service tools. In addition, Leah brings a proven ability to define, improve, and implement process improvement strategies, strong project and vendor management skills and expert time management and project execution skills. \r\n \r\nCurrently, Ms. Pope is serving as a Project Manager on an Implementation project with  Taleo. In this role she provides subject matter expertise of recruiting and onboarding technologies for ATS implementations.\r\n\r\nPrior to Futurestep Consulting, Ms. Pope served as a Senior Analyst, HRIS with The Irvine Company.\r\n', 'Leah Pope', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'leah-pope', '', '', '2011-10-17 14:59:47', '2011-10-17 14:59:47', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1705', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
