(1709, 1, '2011-10-17 15:00:00', '2011-10-17 15:00:00', '<p>Discovering talent with impact is a critical challenge for every successful business – but this a starting point rather than an end itself. Ensuring that your business truly acquires ‘the brightest and the best’ requires an effective assessment and selection strategy, with appropriate processes and technologies in place to deliver time after time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Futurestep draws on its vast experience to help many businesses to analyze their assessment and selection strategies: benchmarking them against best in class organizations; determining their current effectiveness and capacity to grow into new talent segments and new geographies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We focus our consultancy services on the need to deliver improved return on investment and effort. We also understand the need to integrate assessment and selection processes within broader talent management strategies and to maximize the role that technology – career websites and tracking systems to mention just two – can play in improving the way any business assesses and select the best talent.</p>\r\n', 'Candidate Assessment and Selection', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'candidate-assessment-and-selection', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:00:00', '2011-10-17 15:00:00', '', 263, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?page_id=1709', 4, 'page', '', 0),
