(1714, 1, '2011-10-17 15:03:44', '2011-10-17 15:03:44', '<p>Technology has the capacity to transform the way businesses discover and deliver talent, and by its nature it evolves at a rapid rate. Maintaining awareness of ‘what’s out there’ and ‘what’s best for you’ can become a bewildering and time-consuming challenge.</p>\n\n<p>Our experience and sector expertise means that we understand the evolving technology marketplace as well as, if not better, than any business in our industry. We&#39;re excited by the huge potential that technology brings, but realistic about its capabilities. We retain an independent and impartial overview, which means we can advise clients on which technologies are really right for them.</p>\n\n<p> Our technology-focused services include:\n<ul>\n<li>Technology strategy – starting with an assessment of your current technology &#39;footprint&#39;</li>\n<li>Technology sourcing – based on clear definition of needs and independent assessment of available solutions</li>\n<li>Systems implementation and integration – including project management, change management and applications expertise</li>\n<li>System optimization and outsourced support</li>\n</ul>\n</p>', 'Technology Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1713-revision', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:03:44', '2011-10-17 15:03:44', '', 1713, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
