(1737, 1, '2011-10-12 18:20:02', '2011-10-12 18:20:02', 'The Life Sciences practice at Futurestep covers the following sectors; Pharmaceuticals, Medical Devices, Diagnostics, Biotech, Clinical Research Organisations, Consultancies and Service Providers to the Life Science sectors. Within each of the sectors we offer recruitment solutions across all job functions for our clients, these include;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regional &amp; Country Managers</li>\r\n	<li>Medical</li>\r\n	<li>R&amp;D</li>\r\n	<li>Operations</li>\r\n	<li>Sales</li>\r\n	<li>Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Procurement</li>\r\n	<li>HR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur clients range from large Global Corporates to Mid-Size and SME organisations through to Private equity backed and start-up companies. These organisations seek to find, attract, retain and develop high potential talent in order to maintain or gain competitive advantage.\r\n\r\nWe differentiate ourselves by focusing on understanding our Client needs in terms of both functional and cultural fit. Our Consultants have worked within the Life Sciences Markets for many years as recruitment professionals or within the Life Sciences industry itself. This brings an unparallel experience to our teams. Our researchers are multi-lingual and have deep sector experience combined with utilising the best recruitment tools and methodology available within the industry.\r\n\r\nWe are also one of the world‚Äôs largest recruitment services providers operating in the highly competitive life science industry working with a significant proposition of the world‚Äôs leading brands..', 'Life Sciences', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '371-revision-8', '', '', '2011-10-12 18:20:02', '2011-10-12 18:20:02', '', 371, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
