(1745, 1, '2011-10-12 08:22:56', '2011-10-12 08:22:56', 'Our Global Consumer Markets practice at Futurestep covers the broad Consumer sector, ranging from food manufacturing businesses, to consumer electronics and luxury goods. Across this wide area, we recruit across all job functions for our clients including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Country Manager / Managing Director</li>\r\n	<li>Sales</li>\r\n	<li>Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>HR</li>\r\n	<li>Sales</li>\r\n	<li>Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur clients range from large Global Corporates to Mid-Size and SME organisations through to Private Equity-backed and start-up companies. These organisations seek to find, attract, retain and develop high potential talent in order to maintain or gain competitive advantage.\r\n\r\nAs a global leader in recruitment strategy and transformation consulting, Futurestep offers consumer products companies valuable guidance on their talent initiatives and recruitment programmes, every step of the way.\r\n\r\nWe differentiate ourselves by focusing on understanding our Client needs in terms of both functional and cultural fit. Our Consultants have worked within the Consumer Markets for many years as recruitment professionals, which gives us unparalleled experience and credibility within our area. Our researchers are multi-lingual and have deep sector experience combined with utilising the best recruitment tools and methodology available within the industry.', 'Consumer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '365-revision-13', '', '', '2011-10-12 08:22:56', '2011-10-12 08:22:56', '', 365, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
