panies, and <a href="http://www.kornferryinstitute.com/">http://www.kornferryinstitute.com</a> for thought leadership, intellectual property and research.', 'Futurestep Named Top Breadth Of Services Provider In 2011 RPO “Bakers Dozen" Listing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1755-revision-3', '', '', '2011-10-17 15:34:00', '2011-10-17 15:34:00', '', 1755, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
