(1801, 5, '2011-10-17 16:23:34', '2011-10-17 16:23:34', 'Ms. Currie is Vice President and General Manager for Futurestep in Canada. She is responsible for overall leadership, accountability, development and growth of Futurestep''s service lines in Canada, including Search, RPO and Consulting practices. This includes addressing market opportunities, product development, sales, pricing, and service delivery, as well as methodologies, proposals, technology, work processes, quality assurance and best practices.\r\n\r\nPreviously, Ms. Currie was Practice Leader for Futurestep; responsible for leading and managing business development and key client relationships both nationally and globally. She has managed large scale recruitment initiatives in the financial services, consumer, retail, technology and industrial sectors.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ms. Currie was Managing Director of a global technology recruitment and outsourcing consulting firm where she was instrumental in growing the business and delivering numerous strategic projects for clients.\r\n', 'Lyn Currie', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lyn-currie', '', '', '2011-10-17 16:23:34', '2011-10-17 16:23:34', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1801', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
