(1827, 5, '2011-10-18 13:11:21', '2011-10-18 13:11:21', 'Ms. Tong is an experienced Recruiting Team Leader who works closely with a variety of clients in project management, implementation and delivery of Projects and Recruitment Process Outsourcing (RPO)  solutions.\r\n\r\nMost recently, Ms. Tong managed the project for a leading resource & mining client by recruiting more than 20 positions to build up the talent pipeline for their shared service centre in Malaysia. \r\n\r\nShe was also involved in a strategic RPO project for a shared services function for a Solar start-up in Singapore. \r\n\r\nPrior to her current role, her responsibilities were to develop and expand the mid-level management search business, recruit as well as to manage the recruitment team for Futurestep in Singapore. Ms. Tong worked with a diversified client base in Retail, Hospitality, Chemical, Pharmaceutical and Industrial areas.\r\n\r\n', 'May Tong', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'may-tong', '', '', '2011-10-18 13:11:21', '2011-10-18 13:11:21', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1827', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
(1828, 5, '2011-10-18 13:08:58', '2011-10-18 13:08:58', 'Ms. Tong is an experienced Recruiting Team Leader who works closely with a variety of clients in project management, implementation and delivery of Projects and Recruitment Process Outsourcing (RPO)  solutions.\n\nMost recently, Ms. Tong managed the project for a leading resource & mining client by recruiting more than 20 positions to build up the talent pipeline for their shared service centre in Malaysia. \n\nShe was also involved in a strategic RPO project for a shared services function for a Solar start-up in Singapore. \n\nPrior to her current role, her responsibilities were to develop and expand the mid-level management search business, recruit as well as to manage the recruitment team for Futurestep in Singapore. Ms. Tong worked with a diversified client base in Retail, Hospitality, Chemical, Pharmaceutical and Industrial areas.\n\n', 'May Tong', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1827-revision', '', '', '2011-10-18 13:08:58', '2011-10-18 13:08:58', '', 1827, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1829, 5, '2011-10-18 13:15:23', '2011-10-18 13:15:23', 'Mr. Edge is a Consultant in the Industrial sector in Singapore doing end-to-end recruitment. He was previously working in Futurestep’s New Zealand office as the Head of Research.\r\n\r\nJoining Futurestep as a Research Associate in 2006, Mr. Edge progressed in 2008 to the role of Head of Research where he led a team of researchers who supported Futurestep’s consultants across all vertical markets. Mr. Edge has both contributed to and led searches across a range of industry sectors including Manufacturing, Consumer Products, Professional Services, Industrial Services, Retail, Property, Information Technology and Financial Services.\r\n \r\nIn the years prior to joining Futurestep, Mr. Edge held various roles within the mining, mental health and government sectors in Australia and New Zealand. \r\n\r\nMr. Edge holds a Master of Arts degree in Psychology from the University of Otago. \r\n', 'Nigel Edge', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nigel-edge', '', '', '2011-10-18 13:15:23', '2011-10-18 13:15:23', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1829', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
