(1831, 5, '2011-10-18 13:55:36', '2011-10-18 13:55:36', 'Ms. Gossé is a Market Leader based in the Futurestep Singapore office. In this role, she is responsible for middle to senior level management talent acquisition across all industry sectors in the ASEAN region. \r\n\r\nMs. Gossé is passionate about executive search and has established herself as a trusted advisor to both clients and senior level candidates. \r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ms. Gossé was with Alshaya, a leading retail organisation in the Middle East, where she was Senior Executive Recruiter responsible for senior management and executive recruitment. She also led teams in volume retail recruitment projects in the Middle East, Eastern Europe, Russia, Turkey. \r\n\r\nMs. Gossé has a decade of experience in the areas of recruitment and executive search. She has worked for several recruitment firms in both leadership and consultative positions in Lebanon, France and Indonesia, and has also been a Human Resources Manager with LVMH in Paris. \r\n\r\nIn her early career, Ms. Gossé worked for Michael Page and Adecco. In addition to retail, Ms. Gossé has placed candidates in industries such as  automotive, chemical, pharmaceutical, research and Information Technology. \r\n\r\nA French national who is bilingual in English and French, Ms. Gossé holds a Master''s specializing in Marketing and Human Resources Management from the International Business School of Chambery, France. \r\n\r\n \r\n', 'Alice Gossé ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'alice-gosse', '', '', '2011-10-18 13:55:36', '2011-10-18 13:55:36', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1831', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
