(1843, 4, '2011-10-18 15:06:41', '2011-10-18 15:06:41', 'LOS ANGELES, April 11, 2010 – Futurestep, a Korn/Ferry Company (NYSE: KFY) specializing in talent acquisition solutions, will be joining Dell, a leading global provider of technology products, to participate in the 2011 RPO Summit in Las Vegas. At the conference, Futurestep and Dell will present an educational session, “Dell Tackles a High-Pressure Global Recruitment Initiative.”\r\n\r\nIn the session, Jennifer Novit, U.S. Talent Acquisition Manager for Dell, and Laura Eaton, U.S. Director, Recruitment Process Outsourcing (RPO) for Futurestep, will provide insight from Dell’s RPO initiative aimed at meeting sales talent needs under tight timelines. They will cover key considerations for establishing a successful RPO strategy with a global scope, from cultural and regulatory differences, to maintaining consistency and addressing varying local requirements.\r\n\r\nThe presentation will also explore other important factors such as setting expectations, minimizing risks, and overcoming unexpected challenges. “As a leader in a highly competitive industry, Dell understands the vital importance of talent,” says Jennifer Novit of Dell. “Our recruitment strategy addresses the types of needs many enterprise planners face today, and we’re pleased to join our RPO partners at Futurestep to share our success – and our learning – at this year’s summit.”\r\n\r\n“By taking a strategic approach to addressing critical recruitment needs, Dell successfully deployed a global RPO solution that delivered on business goals,” said Laura Eaton, Director, Recruitment Process Outsourcing for Futurestep. “The RPO Summit provides a great resource for anyone who is exploring RPO options to learn first-hand about what it takes to drive an effective RPO strategy.”\r\n\r\nFuturestep will be in attendance throughout the RPO Summit event which takes place May 24-26 at the Venetian Hotel, Resort and Casino in Las Vegas, Nevada. The RPO Summit 2011 is one of four summits taking place at the HRO Today Forum, which unites HR and recruiting change agents and business executives interested in helping to define the future of HR services and technology and how they impact the HR-powered enterprise. The Forum''s other summits are the HRO Summit and the MSP Summit. Learn more at <a href="http://www.rposummit.com/">www.rposummit.com</a>.', 'FUTURESTEP JOINS DELL TO SHARE GLOBAL RPO INSIGHT AT THE 2011 RPO SUMMIT', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'futurestep-joins-dell-to-share-global-rpo-insight-at-the-2011-rpo-summit', '', '', '2011-10-18 15:06:41', '2011-10-18 15:06:41', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=press&#038;p=1843', 0, 'press', '', 0),
