e%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1853, 5, '2011-10-18 14:33:21', '2011-10-18 14:33:21', 'Ms. Wang is a Managing Associate with Futurestep, a Korn/Ferry company, based in Shanghai. As a member of the Industrial practice, Ms. Wang leverages almost 6 years of recruiting experience in placing middle and senior managers within the industry sectors as well as HR positions in multinational and Chinese organisations in Greater China. The positions include sales, marketing, manufacturing and supporting functions.\n\nShe was responsible for the Energy & Utility, Automotive & Transportation, Power, Electrical, Original Equipment Manufacturer and Medical Device industry sectors. In addition, she specialises hiring positions in the HR sectors. \n\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Ms. Wang has worked in global recruitment firms and also a well-known local headhunting firm.\nMs. Wang had significant achievements with 20%-30% annual increase in sales volume and achieved Top Performer twice in her former executive agency. \n\nShe has experience successfully placing more than 70 individuals such as Engineering Manager/Director, HR Manager/HR Director, Sales and Marketing Manager/ Director, Operation Manager/Director, General Manager, Purchasing Manager/Director and others.\n\nMs. Wang started her career as an Executive Assistant in one of the Top 500 French firms. \n\nBorn and raised in Shanghai, Ms. Wang has a Bachelors Degree in Chemical Engineering from Shanghai Normal University. She speaks fluent Mandarin and English.\n', 'Sunny Wang', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1839-revision', '', '', '2011-10-18 14:33:21', '2011-10-18 14:33:21', '', 1839, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/uncategorized/%sub-category%/%page%', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1856, 5, '2011-10-18 15:52:11', '2011-10-18 15:52:11', 'Mr. Yu is a Managing Associate with Futurestep, a Korn/Ferry company, based in Shanghai where he is responsible for strategic talent acquisition. He has experience in executive search, primarily focusing in the Life Sciences field.\r\n\r\nA member of the Life Sciences practice, Mr. Yu brings to Futurestep with over four year of recruitment experience in placing middle and senior managers for multinational and Chinese organisations in Greater China. The positions include Sales, Marketing, Regulatory Affairs, Medical Affairs and other supporting functions.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Futurestep, Mr. Yu was with a local Executive Search company in Shanghai as an Account Manager, where he was in charge of business development and recruitment project management and led a team. \r\n\r\nPrior to his executive search career, Mr. Yu worked as a R&D Supervisor with a joint venture pharmaceutical company. \r\n\r\nBorn and raised in City of Yantai, Mr. Yu holds a Masters Degree in Bioscience from Fudan University. He speaks fluent Mandarin and English. \r\n', 'Vincent Yu', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vincent-yu', '', '', '2011-10-18 15:52:11', '2011-10-18 15:52:11', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=experts&#038;p=1856', 0, 'experts', '', 0),
