(1888, 4, '2011-10-18 16:52:41', '2011-10-18 16:52:41', 'SYDNEY, January 14, 2011 – Futurestep, a Korn/Ferry Company (NYSE: KFY) specialising in talent acquisition solutions, today announced the appointment of Phillipa Eastman as Service Delivery Leader to support its growing solutions business.\r\n\r\nPhillipa Eastman, previously with Chandler Macleod, said "I have been impressed by Futurestep for a number of years and particularly their strong client relationships and the calibre of their people. I feel aligned with the values of the organisation and am excited by their strategic direction. Korn/Ferry has certainly expanded on its search heritage and established itself as a leader in talent solutions."\r\n\r\nFuturestep Australia Managing Director, Sue Tuffley said "Our solutions business continues to grow and Phillipa is a strong addition to our team. As well as having experienced managers onsite with each client, we provide dedicated account managers to ensure that our service levels not only remain consistently high, but also evolve with our client''s business."\r\n\r\nPhillipa added that Futurestep''s integrated approach was a key attraction; "Whilst my focus will be our onsite Client Solutions I will be working alongside colleagues who are specialist experts. I am impressed by Futurestep''s client centric approach. It’s always about finding the right solution which can be anything from an outsourced model, to helping develop an in-house recruitment team, to choosing the right vendors or recruiting a future leader.”', 'PHILLIPA EASTMAN JOINS FUTURESTEP', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phillipa-eastman-joins-futurestep', '', '', '2011-10-18 16:52:41', '2011-10-18 16:52:41', '', 0, 'http://futurestep.testarea.me.uk/?post_type=press&#038;p=1888', 0, 'press', '', 0),
